{"text": "Maintaining Subtree Sizes\n• Need to maintain size attributes during insert and delete \noperations\n• Need to maintain them efficiently, i.e., in            time", "metadata": {"producer": "Acrobat Distiller 25.0 (Windows)", "creator": "PScript5.dll Version 5.2.2", "creationdate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "author": "ruizhang", "moddate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "title": "Microsoft PowerPoint - Lecture-12.pptx", "source": "Lecture-12.pdf", "total_pages": 29, "page": 10, "page_label": "10", "doc_id": "85c63a74-4ccf-459e-b87b-c6c7da6b1e80"}}
{"text": "Insertion\n• During pass downward, we know that the new node will be \na descendant of each node we visit, and only of these nodes. \nTherefore, increment size attribute of each node visited\n• Then there’s the fix-up pass\n• Goes up the tree\n• Changes colors             times\n• Performs at most two rotations\n• Color changes don’t affect subtree sizes.\n• Rotations do!", "metadata": {"producer": "Acrobat Distiller 25.0 (Windows)", "creator": "PScript5.dll Version 5.2.2", "creationdate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "author": "ruizhang", "moddate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "title": "Microsoft PowerPoint - Lecture-12.pptx", "source": "Lecture-12.pdf", "total_pages": 29, "page": 11, "page_label": "11", "doc_id": "85c63a74-4ccf-459e-b87b-c6c7da6b1e80"}}
{"text": "Insertion\n• Determine new sizes based on old sizes and sizes of \nchildren", "metadata": {"producer": "Acrobat Distiller 25.0 (Windows)", "creator": "PScript5.dll Version 5.2.2", "creationdate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "author": "ruizhang", "moddate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "title": "Microsoft PowerPoint - Lecture-12.pptx", "source": "Lecture-12.pdf", "total_pages": 29, "page": 12, "page_label": "12", "doc_id": "85c63a74-4ccf-459e-b87b-c6c7da6b1e80"}}
{"text": "Insertion\n• Similar for right rotation\n• Can update in         time per rotation.  Therefore        time \nspent updating size attributes during fix-up\n• Therefore,            to insert", "metadata": {"producer": "Acrobat Distiller 25.0 (Windows)", "creator": "PScript5.dll Version 5.2.2", "creationdate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "author": "ruizhang", "moddate": "2025-09-29T19:11:27-04:00", "title": "Microsoft PowerPoint - Lecture-12.pptx", "source": "Lecture-12.pdf", "total_pages": 29, "page": 13, "page_label": "13", "doc_id": "85c63a74-4ccf-459e-b87b-c6c7da6b1e80"}}
